<p><span class="catchln" id="secs_12-704a_and_12-704b">Secs. 12-704a and 12-704b. Tax credit for personal property taxes paid on motor vehicles. Tax credit for portion of property tax paid on primary residence or motor vehicle.</span> Sections <a href ="chap_229.htm#sec_12-704a">12-704a</a> and <a href ="chap_229.htm#sec_12-704b">12-704b</a> are repealed, effective July 1, 1997.</p>
