<p><span class="catchln" id="sec_12-709">Sec. 12-709. Exemption under section <a href ="chap_229.htm#sec_12-702">12-702</a> not applicable to trusts or estates. Taxes payable by fiduciary.</span> The tax imposed under this chapter on a trust or estate shall be computed on the Connecticut taxable income of such trust or estate without allowance for any exemption under section <a href ="chap_229.htm#sec_12-702">12-702</a> and shall be paid by the fiduciary.</p>
